node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 13, 2021 tagging @natalyajohnson_. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'You are loved through your good days. You are loved through your bad days. You are loved through your heavy days. You are loved when you are broken. You are loved when you don't have strength. You are loved when you feel like you can't. You are loved when you don't have the energy. You are loved when you don' know which way to turn. You are loved when you can't figure it out. You are loved when you are weak. You are loved through it all. Natalya Johnson'.

node.text:
Repeat after me: You Are Loved ✨ ⠀
(cr: @natalyajohnson_)
